description: Assigns a job membership level to a member.

parameters.name: farmId
parameters.description: The farm ID of the job to associate with the member.

parameters.name: queueId
parameters.description: The queue ID to associate to the member.

parameters.name: jobId
parameters.description: The job ID to associate with the member.

parameters.name: principalId
parameters.description: The member's principal ID to associate with the job.

parameters.name: principalType
parameters.description: The member's principal type to associate with the job.

parameters.name: identityStoreId
parameters.description: The member's identity store ID to associate with the job.

parameters.name: membershipLevel
parameters.description: The principal's membership level for the associated job.
